<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us - Techyevents</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f3f4f6 0%, #ffffff 100%);
            color: #374151;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 2rem;
        }

        .hero {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8b5cf6 0%, #7c3aed 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 4rem 2rem;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .content-section {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 1rem;
            padding: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        h2 {
            color: #7c3aed;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            font-size: 1.8rem;
        }

        .features {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
            gap: 2rem;
            margin-top: 2rem;
        }

        .feature-card {
            background: #f9fafb;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 0.5rem;
            border-left: 4px solid #7c3aed;
        }

        .feature-card h3 {
            color: #7c3aed;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .contact {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 3rem;
            padding: 2rem;
            background: #f9fafb;
            border-radius: 0.5rem;
        }

        .contact a {
            color: #7c3aed;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .contact a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/navbar') %>
    <div class="hero">
        <div class="container">
            <h1>About Techyvents</h1>
            <p>Connecting tech enthusiasts with exciting opportunities</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="content-section">
            <h2>Welcome to Techyvents</h2>
            <p>Your one-stop platform for discovering and accessing the latest tech events! We are dedicated to creating a centralized hub where technology enthusiasts, professionals, and learners can find information about upcoming events, workshops, and conferences in the tech industry.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="content-section">
            <h2>Our Mission</h2>
            <p>Our mission is to foster a vibrant tech community  by providing an easy-to-navigate platform that connects individuals with relevant events. Whether you're looking to enhance your skills, network with like-minded professionals, or stay updated on industry trends, we aim to be your trusted resource.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="content-section">
            <h2>What We Offer</h2>
            <div class="features">
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <h3>Comprehensive Event Listings</h3>
                    <p>Search and explore tech events by category, date, and location.From hackathons to webinars, we've got you covered!</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <h3>User-Friendly Experience</h3>
                    <p>Navigate effortlessly to find events that match your interests.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <h3>Community Engagement</h3>
                    <p>Build valuable connections and collaborate with fellow tech enthusiasts.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="contact">
            <h2>Get in Touch</h2>
            <p>Join us in empowering one another to grow and innovate in the tech industry.</p>
            <p>For inquiries, contact us at <a href="mailto:contact@techyevents.com">contact@techyevents.com</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>